liam-gallagher-john-squire-tracklist-lyrics-3593699">加拉格尔和斯奎尔新专辑的四星评论</a>中， <em>《NME》</em>写道：“如果歌迷对主打单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-gallagher-john-squire-just-another-rainbow-review-3565653">《Just Another Rainbow》</a>感到隐隐约约的惊慌，这首单曲伴随着令人安心的玫瑰风格即兴重复，但也看到利亚姆背诵了彩虹的颜色并思考<i>：“我是你的风车吗？”</i> ，很难想象有人会因为这张专辑本身而感到被欺骗。</p><p> “显然这不是一首‘绝对可能’或‘石玫瑰’——没有人能接触到那些充满魅力的杰作。不过，作为风格和情绪的胜利，《利亚姆·加拉格尔·约翰·斯奎尔》完全配得上他们不朽的遗产。”</p><p>今年晚些时候，加拉格尔将前往<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-oasis-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-uk-tour-dates-tickets-3515369#:~:text=The%202024%20'Definitely%2C%20Maybe',new%20solo%20album%20was%20finished.">参加一系列“Definitely Maybe”30 周年纪念音乐会</a>，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trnsmt-2024-liam-gallagher-gerry-cinmamon-calvin-harris-lead-line-up-3545593#:~:text=lead%20line%2Dup-,TRNSMT%202024%3A%20Liam%20Gallagher%2C%20Gerry%20Cinmamon%2C,Calvin%20Harris%20lead%20line%2Dup&amp;text=Liam%20Gallagher%2C%20Gerry%20Cinnamon%20and%20Calvin%20Harris%20have%20been%20announced,of%20headliners%20at%20TRNSMT%202024.&amp;text=The%20annual%20music%20festival%20will,July%2012%20%2D14%2C%202024.">TRNSMT</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-to-play-oasis-definitely-maybe-in-full-at-reading-leeds-2024-3548140#:~:text=Reading%20%26%20Leeds%202024-,Liam%20Gallagher%20to%20play%20Oasis'%20'Definitely%20Maybe'%20in,full%20at%20Reading%20%26%20Leeds%202024&amp;text=Reading%20%26%20Leeds%20have%20confirmed%20that,headline%20the%20festival%20in%202024.">雷丁和利兹</a>举办头条表演，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-friends-announce-malta-weekender-buy-tickets-3591307">在马耳他举办他的“Liam Gallagher &amp; Friends”周末活动</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-and-john-squire-kick-off-uk-and-ireland-tour-videos-watch-setlist-3600950">观看利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 和约翰·斯奎尔 (John Squire) 在滚石乐队开始英国和爱尔兰巡演时对他们进行报道的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
