es-1032736624-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>女演员奥利瓦·穆恩 (Oliva Munn) 透露，她已被诊断出患有乳腺癌。</p><p>这位<em>《X战警：天启》的</em>主演昨天（3月13日）在社交媒体上宣布了这一消息，透露她在去年4月首次确诊。 Munn 在她的帖子中分享说，去年 2 月，她进行了基因测试，“以积极主动地关注我的健康”。虽然她通过了测试，但两个月后她发现自己患有乳腺癌。</p><p> “在过去的十个月里，我做了四次手术，在床上度过的日子太多了，我什至数不清，并且对癌症、癌症治疗和激素的了解比我想象的要多。”</p><p> “我将诊断、担忧、康复、止痛药和纸质长袍保密。在分享之前，我需要喘口气并完成一些最困难的部分。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4dXfrULDdJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114